Path: Nushell
Content:
NotTheDr01ds worked on SHLVL (
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14732] 1
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14727] 2
), 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14669] added a user-level autoload directory
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14681] removed no-longer-needed 
``convert_env_values``
 calls
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14670] improved 
``open``
 to assign 
``content_type``
 metadata for filetypes not handled with a 
``from``
 converter
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14734] added a comment on 
``nu_repl``
 usage
rikukiix 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14707] made exec command decrement SHLVL correctly & added a SHLVL related test
cptpiepmatz worked on boolean coercion (
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14731] 1
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14704] 2
)
ayax79 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14723] provided the ability to split strings in columns via 
``polars str-split``
ysthakur 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14721] made 
``utouch``
 the new 
``touch``
 and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14717] created a 
``nu_glob::is_glob``
 function
fdncred 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14711] improved error messages for "sum", "product", and "sum_of_squares"
 and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14646] replaced regex crate with fancy_regex
zhiburt 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14710] fixed a 
``tabled``
 panic
sholderbach 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14703] promoted a note about 
``internal_span``
 to doccomment
132ikl 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14700] removed usages of 
``internal_span``
NiceGuyIT 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14696] fixed a command description
0x4D5352 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14695] improved example formatting in README.md
hjetmundsen 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14674] added glob support to 
``utouch``
tsukimizake 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14590] stopped multiline prompts from removing the last newline
